        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe GVNFM use tosca-nfv-v1.0-wd04-rev04 profile. It is not a bug.\nFor the ONAP VNF TOSCA profile is not defined yet. After model subcommittee defined, we will consider how to support it.",
