        "timestamp": "2018-02-11 06:01:35.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n1. in R1, VNFD is not standard in ONAP community, only VNF package structure is standard; What you provided is from the VNF vendors, which is not accepted by the model subcommittee. \n2. Also in R1, VFC do not parse the VNF vendor's package and make it as blackbox\n3. The GVNFM will use the VNFD as I said\n4. In my code review ,what you change is not complete as well.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
